# cvtbase — MNN conversion templates for Local Dream native --convert
#
# Required for MediaTek CLIP export from .safetensors without a QNN/CPU zip.
#
# Obtain cvtbase from a Local Dream APK:
#   unzip LocalDream.apk assets/cvtbase/* -d tools/mtk-convert/cvtbase/
#
# Or from the app build output if you build the project locally.
#
# Expected files include:
#   clip_skip_1.mnn, clip_skip_2.mnn, tokenizer.json, …
